| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3001 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 42235cb0-fcdd-5044-9dc2-2efdf99aa495"
